00:18:15,956 --> 00:18:20,896
I want to lead you down a new path.

241
00:18:20,896 --> 00:18:22,540
A path that will...

242
00:18:22,540 --> 00:18:25,120
bring our people freedom,

243
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:27,662
bring our nation independence,

