313
00:24:10,001 --> 00:24:12,380
- The terrain there is complicated, it gives us an advantage.
- Okay.

314
00:24:12,380 --> 00:24:14,556
- Retreat to the old towns.
- Hurry.

315
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:19,161
Go!

316
00:24:27,978 --> 00:24:31,370
