317
00:24:31,996 --> 00:24:33,106
Give out my order.

318
00:24:33,106 --> 00:24:37,406
Do whatever it takes to kill Tan Xuanlin, even if it means blowing the old towns to dust.

319
00:24:37,406 --> 00:24:39,061
